---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "Terms of use – National Debt Service";
const description =
  "Read the terms of use for the National Debt Service website. We provide general information and signpost to trusted debt advice organisations in the UK.";
const canonicalUrl = "https://www.nationaldebtservice.co.uk/terms";
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description} {canonicalUrl}>
  <main id="main-content" class="bg-primary-50 min-h-screen">
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-10 sm:py-14 space-y-8">
      <header class="space-y-3">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary-700">
          Legal information
        </p>
        <h1>Terms of use</h1>
        <p class="text-base text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          These terms explain how you can use the National Debt Service website. Please read
          them carefully before using the site.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">
          Last updated: 1 December 2025
        </p>
      </header>

      <section aria-labelledby="who-we-are" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="who-we-are" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          1. Who we are
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          National Debt Service is an independent, non-commercial website. We provide general
          information and links to trusted debt advice and mental health support organisations
          across the UK.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          We do not offer debt advice and we are not authorised by the Financial Conduct
          Authority (FCA). Nothing on this site is personal financial, legal or regulated
          advice.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="what-we-do" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="what-we-do" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          2. What this website does
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          This website is designed to help you:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
          <li>understand the different types of free support available in the UK</li>
          <li>find official and regulated organisations that can help</li>
          <li>learn the basics about common money and debt topics</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          We do not:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
          <li>provide personal debt advice or recommend specific products</li>
          <li>contact creditors on your behalf</li>
          <li>act for you in any legal or financial matter</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="not-advice" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="not-advice" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          3. This site is not advice
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          All content on this site is for general information only. It does not take into
          account your personal situation, and it should not be used as a basis for making
          decisions about your debts or finances.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          Before you make any decisions, you should speak to a qualified, authorised debt
          adviser or another regulated professional. You are responsible for any decisions you
          make about your debts.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="external-links" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="external-links" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          4. External links
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          We link to external websites, including government services, charities and other
          support organisations. While we try to keep these links useful and up to date, we
          can’t guarantee:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
          <li>the accuracy or completeness of external content</li>
          <li>that the services they provide are right for you</li>
          <li>that those websites will always be available or secure</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          Following a link to another site is your choice and at your own risk.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="using-content" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="using-content" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          5. Using our content
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          You can read and share links to our pages for personal use. You must not:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
          <li>reuse large parts of our content on another website or service</li>
          <li>present our content as your own work</li>
          <li>suggest that we endorse your organisation, product or service</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="acceptable-use" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="acceptable-use" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          6. Acceptable use
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          You agree not to use this website in any way that:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
          <li>is unlawful, fraudulent or harmful</li>
          <li>attempts to gain unauthorised access to the site or its systems</li>
          <li>introduces viruses, malware or other harmful code</li>
          <li>scrapes or copies the site using automated tools at scale</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="contact-form" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="contact-form" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          7. Contact form
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          If you use the contact form on this site, you agree to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
          <li>provide accurate information</li>
          <li>only contact us about the website itself</li>
          <li>avoid sharing highly sensitive personal details</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          We’ll use your message and contact details only to respond to your query about the
          website, as explained in our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="no-liability" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="no-liability" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          8. No liability
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          We try to keep the site accurate, up to date and available. But we can’t promise it
          will be:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
          <li>error-free</li>
          <li>complete</li>
          <li>always available</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          To the fullest extent allowed by law, we’re not responsible for any loss, damage or
          inconvenience that arises from using this website or relying on its content.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="changes" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="changes" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          9. Changes to these terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          We may update these terms from time to time to reflect changes to the site or the
          law. The date at the top of this page shows when we last updated them.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="contact-us" class="space-y-3">
        <h2 id="contact-us" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          10. How to contact us about these terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-800 leading-relaxed">
          If you have a question or concern about these terms, you can contact us using the{" "}
          <a href="/contact">contact form</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
